      <title>红海危险促使全球石油买家转向本土</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/red-sea-danger-is-spurring-global-oil-buyers-to-go-local</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着红海武装分子袭击和运费飙升使得来自较​​近国家的供应更具吸引力，全球石油市场变得越来越本地化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/red-sea-danger-is-spurring-global-oil-buyers-to-go-local</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从绿色炒作到救助，镍行业已经崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-03/from-green-hype-to-bailouts-the-nickel-industry-has-imploded</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在 18 个月前，全球最大的矿业公司还处于镍矿热潮中。必和必拓集团大张旗鼓地与特斯拉公司达成协议，为其提供电动汽车的关键原料。该公司即将与澳大利亚亿万富翁安德鲁·福雷斯特（Andrew Forrest）争夺全球最有前景的矿山之一的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-03/from-green-hype-to-bailouts-the-nickel-industry-has-imploded</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
